招牌被刮掉，路上有大树被连根拔起，还有车辆被砸。记者从东明县政府办获悉，当地应急、消防、公安等多部门已到现场救援处置，目前受灾情况正在统计中。现场：山东东明县疑遭龙卷风袭击 有建筑受损大树被连根拔起"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d224d61740d2f8bdaedac625d3b0bad1_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "35 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660815567"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Is/nPyNSq9K1QEAMaCTEwOTEyNTQ2MiCZ7Z60BjAAOGpAFnIJNjYwODE1NTY3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1720227312.996870", "card_id": "Q_660492225", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "宇智波斑出走时，宇智波一族的人为什么没有一个人追随他？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "宇智波斑出走时，宇智波一族的人为什么没有一个人愿意追随他？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ef967e4889e277d84897c8f20b2edbcc_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "35 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660492225"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Is/nPyNSq9K1QEAMaCTEwOTA1MzgyMSDp1oy0BjAAOCJAF3IJNjYwNDkyMjI1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1720227312.998060", "card_id": "Q_660739594", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待艾尔登法环 DLC 1.12.3 版本削弱调香瓶和血怪手臂？轮椅削弱后会有玩家破防吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "轮椅不再，还有新的版本之子出现吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-73a3b5a435e19fd22edf87aec909de04_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660739594"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Is/nPyNSq9K1QEAMaCTEwOTEwODU4MCDXgZq0BjAAODBAGHIJNjYwNzM5NTk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": 